🔹 Why CLT is Important

It explains why normal distribution appears everywhere.

Applications:

Statistics

Machine learning

Data analysis

Confidence intervals

🔹 When CLT Applies

Conditions:

1️⃣ Independent observations
2️⃣ Identical distribution
3️⃣ Large sample size (n ≥ 30 usually)

🔹 Important GATE Traps

Thinking original distribution must be normal

Forgetting √n in denominator

Confusing LLN with CLT

